    steps:['Hold infant face-down on your forearm, supporting head.','Give 5 back blows between shoulder blades with heel of hand.','Turn infant face-up, supporting head.','Give 5 chest thrusts with 2 fingers on lower half of sternum.','Repeat until object expelled or infant becomes unconscious.','If unconscious: begin infant CPR (30:2 with 2 fingers), look in mouth before giving breaths.'],
