    tags: ['pinned limb', 'machinery', 'toxins', 'tourniquet'],
    icon: 'fa-cubes',
    warn: '⛔ TOXIC RELEASE — If a limb is crushed for over 30 minutes, releasing the pressure sends deadly potassium and acid to the heart.',
