    donot: [
      'Do NOT assume they are just drunk if they have had access to a garage or automotive chemicals.',
      'Do NOT wait for the "drunk" phase to wear off; the next phase is fatal organ failure.',
      'Do NOT induce vomiting.'
    ],
    seek: 'Requires immediate ER treatment. The antidote is Fomepizole or, ironically, pharmaceutical-grade intravenous ethanol to stop the breakdown of the poison.'
